5
00:01:19,870 --> 00:01:21,120
on this path of revenge,

6
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:24,070
I'll remove the obstacles for you.

7
00:01:24,870 --> 00:01:25,950
Madam Man, Yu…

8
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,840
Su Mingyu is still useful to us.

9
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,150
Su Qichao and Gao Rui colluded

10
00:01:37,350 --> 00:01:38,430
to harm your mother.

11
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:41,510
Su Mingyu must have been sent by Gao Rui.

12
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,430
She's watching your every move

13
00:01:43,710 --> 00:01:45,280
at home and at the company.

14
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:46,710
You must be careful

15
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:48,120
and not let her deceive you.

16
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:49,920
Rest assured.

17
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:52,480
The election for the new chairman is just around the corner.

18
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:53,950
I will reclaim Zhizhen Group,

19
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:56,590
which rightfully belongs to my mother.

20
00:01:57,790 --> 00:01:58,920
Everything they owe her,

21
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:01,760
I'll make them repay tenfold.

22
00:02:02,710 --> 00:02:04,710
I promise.

23
00:02:15,590 --> 00:02:17,750
Han Zhuang, Li Mingqi, Zhao Shude,

24
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,000
Wang He, and Qin Li

25
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,360
are all shareholders

26
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,000
with voting rights in the company.

27
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:25,800
They have old ties with your father

28
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:28,630
but no direct conflicts of interest with you.

29
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:31,560
If you ask, they will support you.

30
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,630
You must convince them

31
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,470
to oppose Xiao Lang's appointment.

32
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,410
- Understood. - Miss Su.

33
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,430
Since when did you become Ms. Gao's assistant?

34
00:02:46,590 --> 00:02:48,150
It's just standard work instructions.

35
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,190
Surely you don't mind, Mr. Xiao?

36
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:52,030
Su Mingyu,

37
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:54,280
I have personal plans today.

38
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,560
You don't need to follow me.

39
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,870
I'm counting on you, Mr. Li.

40
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,150
Don't worry, Yu.

41
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,630
Your father and I were best friends.

42
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:12,840
I need to think it through before I vote.

43
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:14,470
This is non-negotiable.

44
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:15,280
I'm sorry.

45
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,430
I'm really sorry,

46
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,400
but I can't help.

47
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:18,520
I can't agree to that.

48
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:21,560
How could I possibly let Xiao Lang

49
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:22,750
seize the company

50
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:25,400
your father built with a lifetime of hard work?

51
00:03:26,310 --> 00:03:26,870
Thank you.

52
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,650
This election is of great importance

53
00:03:28,710 --> 00:03:30,190
and concerns the company's future development.

54
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,080
