55
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,710
a few words from you.

56
00:03:33,310 --> 00:03:34,470
This is no trivial issue.

57
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,240
Mr. Qin,

58
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,850
I've been waiting here for you all day.

59
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,800
Back when you were caught

60
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,560
in a debt crisis,

61
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,960
