62
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,280
Miss Su,

63
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:48,190
didn't I tell you to get off work on time?

64
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,150
But you still showed up to pick me up.

65
00:03:50,710 --> 00:03:51,360
I'm done.

66
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,470
We can go now.

67
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:54,800
Pleasure working with you.

68
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,470
Mr. Qin,

69
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:05,520
please help me.

70
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:19,380
Do you really want me to step down that badly?

71
00:04:20,210 --> 00:04:22,240
Even if you tricked my father out of all his shares,

72
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,240
you are still unworthy of managing Zhizhen.

73
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:26,920
Besides Gao Rui,

74
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,560
which of your father's old friends

75
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,390
is willing to help you?

76
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:40,630
What are you doing?

77
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:41,390
Let go of me!

78
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,430
Such is human nature.

79
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,270
When someone falls on hard times,

80
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:47,750
others only kick them while they're down and take advantage of their weakness.

81
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:50,190
You expect someone to lend a helping hand,

82
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:53,430
but all they care about is their personal gain.

83
00:04:55,070 --> 00:04:56,190
That's just what you think

84
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:59,070
because all you see is personal gain.

85
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:01,120
But not everyone is like you.

86
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,800
There are surely people in this world who believe

87
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,630
that loyalty is the most precious thing,

88
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,390
something truly worth fighting for.

89
00:05:07,460 --> 00:05:09,470
Yes, personal gain can sway people,

90
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,510
but it will never earn true loyalty.

91
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,600
Loyalty?

92
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,120
How laughable.

93
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,600
